after that states top court rejected the states funding mechanism 
other states where courts overturned school finance systems 
according to a study last year by robert berne associate dean of 
new york universitys graduate school of public administration are 
new jersey kansas wisconsin california connecticut washington 
west virginia wyoming arkansas and montana 
