<TEXT>
as his selfimposed saturday deadline 
approached gov cecil andrus expressed reservations about some 
provisions of what would become the nations most restrictive state 
abortion law 
but he said his concern will not necessarily translate into the 
veto abortion rights activists have been demanding under threats of 
