not hearing enough about the federal 
government roger kranz hopes so and hes prepared to fill the gap 
with gossip news and opinion pieces about the capitals major 
industry 
kranz is launching the washington reporter a new daily 
newspaper to remedy what he sees as a dearth of details about 
